{"tid":1518371,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"麗晶是香港的縮影 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:15:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4add7b75cbd9e5430fe193315b8019a8834f8b98","tid":1518371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190830/20758348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758348&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUipmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=5da936d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758348&h=5d097654\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190830/20758348</a><br />\n<br />\n麗晶是香港的縮影 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190830/large/1567069126_b3fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190830%2Flarge%2F1567069126_b3fb.jpg&h=a8bd9f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣麗晶花園住戶因為穿黑衣回家，被管業處拒諸家門外，有家歸不得。住戶與管業處理論，更被警察入內干預，兩名住戶被捕並被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n事件引發住戶不滿，過千居民出席座談會，要求管業處交代事件，這一次，來了60個白衣人監場「維持秩序」，費用由管理費支付。不知道管業處在批出這筆費用前，有沒有徵詢過業主的同意？<br />\n<br />\n用你的錢來對付你，侵犯你的人權、剝奪你維護自己權利的自由，麗晶花園，根本就是今日香港的縮影。加害香港人，剝奪我們的人權和自由，侵害我們生命安全，一手摧毁我們家園的特首、高官、警隊，哪一個不是由我們納稅人支付薪酬？<br />\n<br />\n造成今日麗晶局面的，業主有不可推卸的責任，多年來，有沒有認真參與屋苑大小事務？有沒有出席業主大會？相信不止是麗晶花園的業主，很多其他屋苑的業主都甚少關注屋苑事務。正如過去多年，很多香港不關心政治，甚至以政治冷感為榮，不投票或胡亂投票，覺得異見者的聲音破壞社會表面的和諧。一覺睡醒，才發現香港已經變得面目全非。羅馬不是一日建成的，香港爛到骨子裏，當然也不是一朝一夕的事。<br />\n<br />\n我們以為我們失去的是穿甚麼衣服上街的自由，原來，連穿甚麼衣服回家的自由也已經失去。香港人，除了抗爭，還有別的出路嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n漏氣、露餡、半點不由人 (蔣芸)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n論「反送中」 (古德明)"},{"pid":"e4c7c474bc872c44249bca97f59c3c768a9630b6","tid":1518371,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>九二九三 全港三罷 不見不散</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO6ZAhe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO6ZAhe.jpg&h=19f5bbb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f143ccd3de3d7c1ba5fd33b68310224c7c9f99e3","tid":1518371,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUipmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b228c56c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUipmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=db2890c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUipmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=2c287d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"b45402a74a09ee4a950c7b5a6217e507cb4c78a8","tid":1518371,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"高慧然轉咗死性呀<img s